Module com.vexed.vexed
Package com.comp2059.app.controller

Class PrimaryStageController

java.lang.Object
com.comp2059.app.controller.PrimaryStageController
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class PrimaryStageController extends Object implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
This controller is to control primary stage. When user click the buttons, display the sound and do the corresponding actions. When user's mouse enters the buttons, the button's opacity will be smaller. When user's mouse exits the buttons, the button's opacity will be restored. When user click the checkboxes or images, change the checkboxes' status to 'selected' and others to 'not selected'. User can click the trumpet pattern to set the sound on or off.
Since:
9 November 2022
